overview:
Serial internet entrepreneur based out of Seattle.

CEO and founder of ActiveRain.com, a social network and blogging platform for the real estate industry. ActiveRain received $2.75M in Series A financing from MarketLeader (LEDR), employs 30 employees (Feb 2011), is profitable, and receives over 3M monthly visitors to its network of websites.

Jonathan launched DailyTicket in February 2011 in the founding CEO role. DailyTicket is a daily deals site that is based on an franchise model with exclusive territories offered to the franchise owners.
